- I'm here in one of the most
special places on the planet

00:00:08.770 --> 00:00:10.470
because there's a natural phenomenon

00:00:10.470 --> 00:00:12.960
that occurs here and nowhere else.

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:15.650
I'm Phil Torres, Atlas Obscura tour guide,

00:00:15.650 --> 00:00:17.990
researcher, and science communicator.

00:00:17.990 --> 00:00:19.630
And today, I'm leading a group through

00:00:19.630 --> 00:00:22.960
the butterfly sanctuaries
