of monarch butterflies

00:00:25.580 --> 00:00:28.692
migrate every year to spend the winter.

00:00:28.692 --> 00:00:31.080
And the history behind
the scientific discoveries

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:33.230
and the significance to the local culture

00:00:33.230 --> 00:00:37.730
