00:01:10.010 --> 00:01:13.010
- The way the story of the
discovery of these places

00:01:13.010 --> 00:01:16.600
gets told is that it was in the mid-1970s

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.190
when people finally figured out where

00:01:18.190 --> 00:01:20.260
the monarch butterflies went every winter.

00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:21.840
That story is

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:26.400
not untrue, but it ignores
the part where all the people

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:29.590
who lived in these places were aware

00:01:29.590 --> 00:01:34.590
that monarch butterflies showed
up every year in the winter.

