The trees are just orange,
they're like carpeting.

00:02:05.701 --> 00:02:07.633
Look back there, it's amazing!

00:02:10.922 --> 00:02:11.755
Wow!

00:02:11.755 --> 00:02:13.750
That's me, Joe Hanson, biologist,

00:02:13.750 --> 00:02:15.670
science communicator, and YouTuber.

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:17.360
I've been fascinated by the story of

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:20.410
the monarch butterfly and
